Package pool.poolModel

Class Vector

java.lang.Object
pool.poolModel.Vector
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Vector extends Object implements Serializable
This class represents a mathematical Vector with its arithmetic operations. Vectors are elements of the linear algebra and indicate in which way a point can be parallel displaced.
